word_mean_info__list.difference: 侧重以过去经验或根据现实的某些感觉把某事认定为是事实。
常用词，意义较广泛，指缺乏确切事实，根据一些现象进行的推测，也可指为论证而提出合乎逻辑推理的某种假定，有时仅表示自己的意见。
常用词，指毫无根据仅凭个人主观臆断或碰运气的猜测。
指为证实一个理论的正确性而进行的假设。
指有很少或完全无根据的武断推测或不合逻辑的推理。

bilingual.source: I presume you have finished your homework.
bilingual.target: 我假定你已经完成了作业。

bilingual.source: Do not presume to know what I am thinking.
bilingual.target: 不要假定你知道我在想什么。

bilingual.source: Let's presume that everything will go as planned.
bilingual.target: 让我们假定一切都会按计划进行。

bilingual.source: I presume that someone is presuming a joke.
bilingual.target: 我们必须假定他们是无罪的。

bilingual.source: I presume you want to do your best when you sit down at a poker table.
bilingual.target: 当你坐到扑克桌上时，我假定你想做到最好。

bilingual.source: You can't presume to know where the needs are. You can't locate time poverty.
bilingual.target: 你不能假定自己知道大众的需求在哪里。你无法定位时间匮乏的地方。

bilingual.source: I presume then that you are going to make one of the interdicted answers?
bilingual.target: 这样的话，我假定你可以从被禁止的答案中选择一个作为答案，又如何？

bilingual.source: Is it reasonable to presume they would have wanted to provide the reward of citizenship to the children of the violators of those laws?
bilingual.target: 他断言“假定他们愿意给限制移民法律违法者的子女提供公民权合理吗？

bilingual.source: But most of us are reluctant to start these conversations because we presume the opposite.
bilingual.target: 但是我们大多数人都不愿意开始这样的谈话，因为我们的设想与之截然相反。

yingyinNormal.en: The culprit has been identified, I presume? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想凶手已经逮到了吧，是吗？是啊。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Don't presume to tell me what I will and will not do. You don't know me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你凭什么说我会不会去做什么? 你又不认识我。

yingyinNormal.en: So, am I to presume that her flirtation was just a sales technique? I think so.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以，我可以推测她挑逗我只是销售技巧的一种罢了？应该是。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, you know, when the CIA, I presume that's who you're working for. The CIA. Am I right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 无所谓了，当中情局，我假设你们为中情局干活儿，中情局，我猜得对吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm honoured to have as my patroness Lady Catherine de Bourgh. You've heard of her, I presume?
yingyinNormal.zh: 能有位像凯瑟琳·德·包尔夫人那样的女资助人是我三生有幸。我想你们已经听说她了吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. I presume the tapes are in my office. Your office? Cast your mind back. It used to be yours.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是。我想录像应该在我办公室吧。你的办公室？回想一下。那里原本是你的。

yingyinNormal.en: I would not presume to educate you on the wiles of political men, comely or otherwise, Chancellor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论如何，我可不敢冒昧教您如何做一个智谋多端的政客，宰相大人。

yingyinNormal.en: I wouldn't presume to know what President Petrov is thinking. I'll know more once we have a chance to speak.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不会妄加揣测佩特罗夫总统的想法，等我们有机会谈过以后我会知道更多。

yingyinNormal.en: Dr. Turtleneck, I presume. How could you tell? Oh, because you just seem like a doctor to me. Thank you. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我猜你就是龟颈博士吧。你怎么看出来的？因为...我看你就觉得像博士。谢谢你 。也谢谢你。

yingyinNormal.en: Would it be so bad? The only poet peer I am familiar with is Lord Byron. And I presume you all know how that ended.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那很糟糕吗？我唯一熟悉的贵族诗人就是拜伦勋爵。我想你该知道他的下场吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, I presume we're done. Or is this "putting us in mortal danger" situation gonna be a regular thing? No. We're done.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我猜我们是搞定了，还是说以后“置身死地”将成为家常便饭。不，我们搞定了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh my dear, where shall I start? Suppose the farmer talks? Suppose you're seen visiting his home, which I presume is the idea?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊，我该从何说起？如果农民开始议论纷纷呢？假如你被看到去他家，我想你就是这么打算的吧？

yingyinNormal.en: So many days not lived, so many words unsaid, et cetera, et cetera, et cetera, et cetera... Yes, yes, yes, and this, I presume, will be their coffin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有那么久的人生，还有那么多未说出口的话，等等，等等，等等，等等……没错，我猜这将会是那人的棺材。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: But most of us are reluctant to start these conversations because we <highlight>presume</highlight> the opposite.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是我们大多数人都不愿意开始这样的谈话，因为我们的设想与之截然相反。

examination_example.sentence: The report <highlight>presumes</highlight> that "traditional diets" in countries like India include little red meat.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该报告推测，在印度等国家，“传统饮食”包括少量红肉。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: These approaches, however, often <highlight>presume</highlight> less food literacy among low-income people.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，这些方法通常认定低收入人群的食品知识水平较低。
